PrecisAppointment of Mr. Justice Herbert B. Morgan, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Newfoundland, as Temporary Administrator of the Government of Newfoundland, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor over the course of three brief periods in May, June and July 1990 (May 30 - June 1; June 19 - 21; June 26 - July 2).
